# Always Run Plan Reviewer

When creating a new plan or updating an existing plan, always run the `plan-reviewer` subagent before finalizing the plan.

## Required Workflow

1. Draft or revise the plan content.
2. Invoke the `plan-reviewer` subagent to review the latest plan.
3. Incorporate critical and high-severity feedback into the plan.
4. Present the updated plan only after review feedback has been addressed or explicitly deferred with rationale.

## Enforcement Notes

- This rule applies to every planning task.
- Do not skip `plan-reviewer` even for minor plan updates.
